content: Gefal Keb was a Gossam senior civil servant in the Public Protection Department of the Galactic Alliance government on Coruscant. During the Second Galactic Civil War, Keb provided Admiral Cha Niathal with information from the Coruscant Security Force  on threats to the GA or other internal intelligence.
